OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,FWatch as Emma Webber and the parents
OL,8,Fof Grace O'Malley-Kumar, Dr Sanjoy
OL,9,FKumar and Dr Sinead O'Malley-Kumar,
OL,10,Fdemand those responsible for these
OL,11,Ffailings, such as the medics, be held
OL,12,Fto account.
OL,14,FThe families of the three victims of
OL,15,Fthe 2023 Nottingham attacks say "every
OL,16,Fsingle agency failed", as they held a
OL,17,Fpress conference today, after the end
OL,18,Fof evidence at the public inquiry.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,FGrandfather Ian Coates and students
OL,8,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,9,FKumar were all stabbed by paranoid
OL,10,Fschizophrenic Valdo Calocane.
OL,12,FThe triple killer was sectioned four
OL,13,Ftimes, before he also seriously
OL,14,Finjured Wayne Birkett, Sharon Miller
OL,15,Fand Marcin Gawronski with a van,
OL,16,Fduring his violent rampage in
OL,17,FNottingham on June 13th 2023.
OL,19,FAll the families were critical of the
OL,20,F"attitude" of those who gave evidence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,FBarnaby's mother Emma Webber described
OL,8,Fit as "arrogance" and "evasiveness",
OL,9,Fwith witnesses offering up "a lot of
OL,10,Fexcuses" for people who "aren't doing
OL,11,Ftheir jobs.
OL,13,FMr Coates' three sons were at the
OL,14,Fpress conference in London today,
OL,15,Falongside Barnaby and Grace's parents.
OL,17,FThe inquiry lifted the lid on a
OL,18,Fcatalogue of failings by multiple
OL,19,Fagencies and missed opportunities,
OL,20,Fwhich the families say show their
OL,21,Floved ones' deaths were avoidable.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,FThe families said they are "one
OL,8,Ffamily" now, having grieved together
OL,9,Fand fought so hard together for
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,FEmma Webber, who asked "Why are we not
OL,8,Fseeing heads roll?" is now calling for
OL,9,Fa meeting with the Prime Minister,
OL,10,FAttorney-General, Health Secretary and
OL,11,FJustice Secretary next month to demand
OL,12,Fchanges now.
OL,14,FThe families say there needs to be
OL,15,Faction now before the Inquiry chair
OL,16,FHer Honour Deborah Taylor publishes
OL,17,Fher report next year.
OL,19,FJames Coates, son of Ian, told the
OL,20,Fpress conference:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,F"The evidence I've heard at the
OL,8,FInquiry has utterly astounded and
OL,9,Fdisgusted me".
OL,11,FHe said agencies need to be pro-active
OL,12,Fin making changes, saying "it feels
OL,13,Flike the institutions are waiting to
OL,14,Fbe told".
OL,16,F"We want accountability"
OL,18,FHis brother Darren Coates said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,F"We want accountability ... we want
OL,8,Faction against these public servants
OL,9,F.. we will not stop "until we get
OL,10,Fjustice for our loved ones".
OL,12,FBarnaby's mother Emma Webber told the
OL,13,Fwhole press conference it was ITV News
OL,14,FCentral's Political Correspondent
OL,15,FAlison Mackenzie, who secured the
OL,16,Fpublic inquiry, by "ambushing the
OL,17,FPrime Minister".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,FThe final witness giving evidence on
OL,8,Fthe last day of the inquiry last week
OL,9,Falso said the survivors of the attacks
OL,10,Fdid not receive their basic rights as
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,FWayne Birkett, Sharon Miller, and
OL,14,FMarcin Gawronski all survived the
OL,15,Fattacks.
OL,17,FThey sustained serious, life-changing
OL,18,Finjuries after being struck by a van
OL,19,Fdriven by Calocane.
OL,21,FHow have the agencies named responded?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781093477
OL,3,CNottingham Inquiry: Families on
OL,4,C'catastrophic collapse of
OL,5,Cresponsibility'
OL,7,FLeicestershire Police said in a
OL,8,Fstatement:
OL,10,F"As the IOPC investigation is still
OL,11,Fongoing, we are unable to provide any
OL,12,Fcomment or facilitate any requests for
OL,13,Finterview".
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police said in a
OL,16,Fstatement:
OL,18,F"We remain committed to supporting the
OL,19,FInquiry and will fully consider any
OL,20,Frecommendations made".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
